row.question: A class of 10 students is having an average age of 15, another group of 4 students whose average age is 12 has been added to them. What is the average of the new group formed?
row.rationale:
sum of ages of the new group formed= (15x10) + (4x12) = 198
Total number of people in the new group= 10+4= 14
Average of the new group=198/14 = 14.14
Answer: C
